# Environment and secrets
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example
**/app/core/secret/*.json
**/credentials.json
**/token.json
**/client_secret.json

# Dependency folders
**/node_modules/
**/.venv/
**/venv/
**/.pnpm-store/

# Next.js / frontend build output
**/.next/
**/out/
**/.turbo/
**/next-env.d.ts

# Expo / React Native generated state
**/.expo/
**/.expo-shared/
**/web-build/
**/android/.gradle/
**/android/app/build/
**/android/build/
**/ios/Pods/
**/ios/build/
